1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,200
Did you know your cells have tiny factories?

2
00:00:03,200 --> 00:00:04,400
They're called ribosomes!

3
00:00:04,400 --> 00:00:08,400
These molecular machines read RNA, the instructions for building proteins.

4
00:00:08,400 --> 00:00:13,600
They grab amino acids, the building blocks of life, and piece them together.

5
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:18,800
Each ribosome can create a protein in just minutes, crucial for cell function.

6
00:00:18,800 --> 00:00:23,600
Without ribosomes, our cells would be lifeless, unable to perform essential tasks.

7
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:26,400
Want to dive deeper into cell biology?

8
00:00:26,400 --> 00:00:28,000
Hit that follow button!
